Network:
- handle all network stuffs
- handle routing
- bandwidth measurement

Peer class:
- handle messages from Network

FileEntry class:
- perms
- name

DirEntry (derived from FileEntry) class:
- filelist

Cache class:
- containt the '/' DirEntry
- does all I/O to the HDD
- interface to fuse

Config class:
- store the ip of one peer
